<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-9806A531-8172-427C-A0B4-5DBC97FA13B6" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-9806A531-8172-427C-A0B4-5DBC97FA13B6" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title translate="no" class="- topic/title "> Task Upgrade White [Tasks]</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">SDS</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p "> Configuration, verification and calibration after the white hardware is installed. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-CAB53886-53D4-4E0F-B6E4-F23235AF7530" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> Precondition</title><p class="- topic/p ">Ink Cabinet accessible, white ink pump connected AND white printhead installed. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-9FF1EF74-AF49-41F5-A1D0-36D741F8096C" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Steps:</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the ink cabinet and be sure you have access to the green luer of the recirculation tube. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Be sure a temporary waste bin is available to support white ink coming out from the green luer tube. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Execute the action "whiteInkHardwareInstalled" and "Recirculate ink" from the action list below. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Set the correct media thickness of when using the service media via task[A] 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Load calibration media on roll position 1 via the LUI. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Set the winding mode is set to 'OFF' via the LUI. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Finish the remaining actions from the list below. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">8. Print the PQT White Specialty via task[D]. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Optional: Print the demoprint via the UI. (Includes white demoprint as last print) 
</p></li></ol><note id="GUID-42E9BB44-CAF9-4FA7-82EA-462C6D3F81DD" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Set the winding method to "OFF" (via service user mode -&gt; output -&gt; select 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">winding mode: no</b>). 
</p></note><note id="GUID-A9B9AA7E-5C4F-42A2-A16B-C84347C65525" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> If new PH's are installed (which is the case during this upgrade) ORE270001 always pops up to be able to check if the ink valves are open. This ORE happens as soon as the printheads reached their temperature. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-B5DE307A-FF20-447C-B5EE-5A8308A33CB4" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/></section><section id="GUID-B9367F3E-4D8C-4B8B-8CAE-5EAEF87C230A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><p class="- topic/p "> Execute the steps below: 
</p><table id="GUID-055F5617-BE50-49EC-BCA8-279AB6AD7661" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.01*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="1.01*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="1.02*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="1.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">SDS test 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Description 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS02-1-007" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0A54BE35-DD2E-4DD3-B683-1BE73711726B.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02-1-007 White Ink Hardware Installed?>02-1-007 White Ink Hardware Installed</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Set WhiteInkHardwareInstalled to 1.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">leave SDS and restart the engine.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">White ink must be loaded before execution, check the normal user mode for the status on the white ink. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS2-6-010" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-E303C6AD-478F-4ED5-A1EC-2A3DEFB936C7.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 2-6-010 White Ink Recirculation (Special Test)?>02-6-010 White Ink Recirculation (Special Test)</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Verify that white ink is pumped into the temporary waste bin. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This can take upto 10 minutes. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><note id="GUID-297FBA46-8F1B-404E-A8B2-195068EF4019" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> This can take up to 25 minutes due to the warming up and repeating cleaning actions of the heads.
</p></note></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS04-6-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-80EF4539-4481-4CD3-9E0E-62465202BFA9.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 04-6-002 Get nozzle status [Special Tests]?>04-6-002 Get nozzle status [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if 1 the white printhead contains more than 5 air nozzles. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS07-6-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0B61ECEF-7439-4133-9F7C-06783020D8CF.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 07-6-002 Clean the printheads (one pulse + wipe action) [Special Tests]?>07-6-002 Clean the printheads (one pulse + wipe action) [Special Tests]</xref>
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Execute 3 x a powerful pressure pulse if more than 5 air nozzles. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS21-6-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-D650BDBB-4674-4B96-BD64-98FDD9BAF4CB.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-002 Select required printer calibrations [Special Tests]?>21-6-002 Select required printer calibrations [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Select required calibrations. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Select for a upgrade: 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> M&amp;C scanner, Carriage Y and printhead nozzle optimization 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS04-6-026" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-4902F798-1908-49CF-82FB-68AF68630957.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 04-6-026 Execute printhead calibrations [Special Tests]?>04-6-026 Execute printhead calibrations [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Execute the printhead calibrations. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS21-6-003" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-B828E436-A124-4809-981E-2DBE1E09A388.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-003 Execute selected printer calibrations [Special Tests]?>21-6-003 Execute selected printer calibrations [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Execute the remaining engine calibrations. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS04-6-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-80EF4539-4481-4CD3-9E0E-62465202BFA9.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 04-6-002 Get nozzle status [Special Tests]?>04-6-002 Get nozzle status [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if the new printhead fulfills the requirements. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-3AD12DA3-F651-4B11-BEB9-FD79AA9649BB.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>SDS</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
